            <div class="rc-sdot"><span class="rc-sdot-dot" style="animation-delay:1.5s"></span>ASP.NET Core</div>
            <div class="rc-sdot"><span class="rc-sdot-dot" style="animation-delay:2.1s"></span>MS SQL /SSMS</div>
