</section>

<!-- ═══ ABOUT ═══ -->
<section id="about" class="rc-fade">
    <p class="section__text__p1">Who I Am</p>
    <h1 class="title">Here's What I Solve<br/>For Your Business</h1>

    <div class="section-container">
        <!--
        <div class="about-left-column">
            <div class="about-education-center">
                <div class="details-container education-card">
                    <img src="~/assets/icons/mortarboard.svg" alt="Education Icon" class="icon" />
                    <h3></h3>
                    <p>
                       
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        -->

        <div class="about-details-container">
            <div class="text-container">
                
                <p>
                    As a Software Developer, I build web systems that don't just look good — they <em>operate</em>.
                    I architect solutions that handle real traffic, integrate AI intelligently, and connect seamlessly
                    to your existing tools and APIs.
                </p>
                <p>
                    I work with startups, small businesses, churches, and nonprofits who need a developer that
                    communicates clearly, ships on time, and understands that technology is only valuable when
                    it solves a human problem.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Whether you need a client-facing web app, an AI-powered tool that automates your workflow,
                    or a custom API that ties your systems together — I scope it, build it, and deliver it production-ready.
                </p>

                <div class="rc-stat-row">
                    <div class="rc-stat-card rc-glass hud-brackets">
                        <span class="rc-stat-num">3+</span>
                        <span class="rc-stat-label">Years Building</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="rc-stat-card rc-glass hud-brackets">
                        <span class="rc-stat-num">AI</span>
                        <span class="rc-stat-label">Integrated Apps</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="rc-stat-card rc-glass hud-brackets">
                        <span class="rc-stat-num">24h</span>
                        <span class="rc-stat-label">Response Time</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="rc-stat-card rc-glass hud-brackets">
                        <span class="rc-stat-num">100%</span>
                        <span class="rc-stat-label">Remote Ready</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <a href="#services" aria-label="Scroll to Services">
        <img src="~/assets/icons/arrow-down-square.svg" alt="" class="icon arrow" />
    </a>
</section>

<!-- ═══ SERVICES ═══ -->
<section id="services" class="rc-fade">
    <p class="section__text__p1">What I Offer</p>
    <h1 class="title">Services</h1>
    <div class="rc-services-grid">

        <div class="rc-service-card rc-glass hud-brackets">
            <div class="rc-service-header">
                <span class="rc-service-icon">🌐</span>
                <div class="rc-service-title">Enterprise Web Applications</div>
            </div>
            <p class="rc-service-desc">Engineering secure, performant, and high-availability full-stack web applications utilizing ASP.NET Core, Blazor, and modern SPA frameworks like React. Designed with clean architecture patterns, robust state management, and containerized deployments across AWS, GCP, or Azure.</p>
            <div class="rc-tags"><span class="rc-tag">ASP.NET Core</span><span class="rc-tag">React</span><span class="rc-tag">Docker</span><span class="rc-tag">Blazor</span><span class="rc-tag">Clean Architecture</span><span class="rc-tag">CI/CD</span></div>
        </div>

        <div class="rc-service-card rc-glass hud-brackets">
            <div class="rc-service-header">
                <span class="rc-service-icon">🤖</span>
                <div class="rc-service-title">Cognitive Systems &amp; GenAI Pipelines</div>
            </div>
            <p class="rc-service-desc">Architecting and integrating intelligent capabilities into enterprise workflows. Designing Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) pipelines, building orchestration layers, integrating OpenAI/Anthropic APIs or open-source LLMs, and implementing automated semantic search and intelligent document processing.</p>
            <div class="rc-tags"><span class="rc-tag">OpenAI / Anthropic</span><span class="rc-tag">RAG</span><span class="rc-tag">Semantic Search</span><span class="rc-tag">Vector DBs</span><span class="rc-tag">C#</span><span class="rc-tag">Python</span></div>
        </div>

        <div class="rc-service-card rc-glass hud-brackets">
            <div class="rc-service-header">
                <span class="rc-service-icon">⚡</span>
                <div class="rc-service-title">RESTful &amp; GraphQL API Engineering</div>
            </div>
            <p class="rc-service-desc">Building secure, scalable, and fully-documented APIs to unify front-ends, mobile clients, and third-party integrations. Engineered with OAuth2/OpenID Connect, rate limiting, distributed caching (Redis), API Gateways, and relational/NoSQL database layers.</p>
            <div class="rc-tags"><span class="rc-tag">REST</span><span class="rc-tag">GraphQL</span><span class="rc-tag">OAuth2 / OIDC</span><span class="rc-tag">Redis</span><span class="rc-tag">OpenAPI / Swagger</span><span class="rc-tag">PostgreSQL</span></div>
        </div>

        <div class="rc-service-card rc-glass hud-brackets">
            <div class="rc-service-header">
                <span class="rc-service-icon">⛪</span>
                <div class="rc-service-title">Nonprofit &amp; Community Digital Solutions</div>
            </div>
            <p class="rc-service-desc">Designing secure, highly accessible (WCAG compliant) web platforms for churches and nonprofit organizations. Integrated with secure PCI-compliant payment gateways (Stripe/PayPal), content management systems (CMS), custom event scheduling, and real-time interactive maps.</p>
            <div class="rc-tags"><span class="rc-tag">Accessibility (WCAG)</span><span class="rc-tag">Stripe / PayPal</span><span class="rc-tag">CMS</span><span class="rc-tag">Event Calendars</span><span class="rc-tag">SEO</span></div>
        </div>

        <div class="rc-service-card rc-glass hud-brackets">
            <div class="rc-service-header">
                <span class="rc-service-icon">🔧</span>
                <div class="rc-service-title">Infrastructure Management &amp; SRE</div>
            </div>
            <p class="rc-service-desc">Providing proactive system reliability engineering (SRE), root-cause analysis, and infrastructure support. Deploying log aggregation (ELK, Datadog), continuous system monitoring, writing runbooks, and configuring network/OS-level security controls.</p>
            <div class="rc-tags"><span class="rc-tag">SRE</span><span class="rc-tag">Log Aggregation</span><span class="rc-tag">Monitoring</span><span class="rc-tag">Linux / Windows Admin</span><span class="rc-tag">Security Auditing</span></div>
        </div>

        <div class="rc-service-card rc-glass hud-brackets">
            <div class="rc-service-header">
                <span class="rc-service-icon">🚀</span>
                <div class="rc-service-title">Cloud Infrastructure &amp; CI/CD Pipelines</div>
            </div>
            <p class="rc-service-desc">Automating code deployment pipelines and cloud infrastructure provisioning. Authoring infrastructure-as-code (IaC), setting up GitHub Actions for automated unit testing and build verification, orchestrating Docker containers, and configuring SSL/TLS certificates and load balancers.</p>
            <div class="rc-tags"><span class="rc-tag">GitHub Actions</span><span class="rc-tag">IaC (Terraform)</span><span class="rc-tag">Docker</span><span class="rc-tag">Kubernetes</span><span class="rc-tag">SSL/TLS</span><span class="rc-tag">Load Balancers</span></div>
        </div>

    </div>
    <a href="#process" aria-label="Scroll to Process">
        <img src="~/assets/icons/arrow-down-square.svg" alt="" class="icon arrow" />
    </a>
</section>

<!-- ═══ PROCESS ═══ -->
<section id="process" class="rc-fade">
    <p class="section__text__p1">How It Works</p>
    <h1 class="title">Project Lifecycle</h1>
    <div class="rc-process-steps">
        <div class="rc-process-step rc-glass">
            <div class="rc-step-num">01</div>
            <div class="rc-step-title">Discovery</div>
            <p class="rc-step-desc">Free scope call. We define your goals, requirements, timeline, and budget before any work begins.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rc-process-arrow">→</div>
        <div class="rc-process-step rc-glass">
            <div class="rc-step-num">02</div>
            <div class="rc-step-title">Design</div>
            <p class="rc-step-desc">Architecture plan, UI wireframe, tech stack confirmation. You approve before I build anything.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rc-process-arrow">→</div>
        <div class="rc-process-step rc-glass">
            <div class="rc-step-num">03</div>
            <div class="rc-step-title">Build</div>
            <p class="rc-step-desc">Iterative development with regular updates. You see progress — no black box, no surprises.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rc-process-arrow">→</div>
        <div class="rc-process-step rc-glass">
            <div class="rc-step-num">04</div>
            <div class="rc-step-title">Launch</div>
            <p class="rc-step-desc">Production deployment, testing, handoff docs, and 30-day post-launch support included.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

